  <h1>The 7-Step Blueprint for Building LLM Agents That <em>Actually</em> Work</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Everyone's building agents. Most are held together with duct tape. Here's the engineering framework that treats agentic systems like real software.</p>
  <p class="hero-meta">Lorenzo Xiao &middot; Language Technologies Institute, CMU &middot; March 2026</p>
