<div class="callout warn">
  <div class="callout-title">Watch for Population-Level Blindspots</div>
  <p>An increase in the average metric does not guarantee all users see improvement. The arithmetic mean prioritizes the largest subgroup, potentially at the expense of marginalized groups. Always disaggregate by user expertise, language, cultural context, and platform. An agent that works well for power users but fails for novices has a quality-of-service problem, even if average metrics look great.</p>
