<p>Set up severity tiers: P0 for safety incidents (immediate rollback), P1 for major regressions (1-hour response), P2 for minor issues (1-day). Assign on-call owners. Run quarterly fire drills. A practical rule of thumb: if a single agent triggers more than 10 downstream calls, investigate.</p>

